==== SOURCE

https://www.wired.com/story/amazon-alexa-2018-machine-learning/	

==== AGENT

Amazonâ€™s Alexa team

==== GOAL

Create a more conversational virtual assistant which helps users without introducing new frustrations.

==== DATA

There data came from users.

==== METHODS

They used a machine learning method called active learning in which the system identifies areas it needs help from a human expert. They also managed to have the system understand string requests without needing to use the keyword again.

==== RESULTS

The result was a more conversational relationship between users and the system in which the system understands requests better.
